Octapi Stack 3 towers of 3 

Tower 1  
Module 1 
Hardware 
- Pi 3B+
- camera module and pimoroni pan and tilt+ 
- hdmi to tv
- usb Mic 
- 3.5 speaker to dancing speakers
OS - Operating Systems 
- Kodi
- Raspbian google aiy version

# Module 2  
Hardware 
- USB Camera x 2 
- HDMI Cable TV + Sound
- USB Mic
OS 
- Kodi
- Raspbian aiy 
Software
curlmount
dejavu?backup
virtualenv
motioneye
raspbian google aiy

# Module 3 
Hardware
- Screen 3.5 Inch  + 
usb Gooseneck Mic
USB EWA Speaker
USB Camera x 2 
OS -
- raspbian
- raspbian port
software  
 - motioneye
- set up to Cameras to record x 3 mininum + record to NAS

